    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "cas_text",
      "x": 1036,
      "y": 162,
      "width": 532,
      "height": 268,
      "text": "CASConflictError attributes:\n  key             str    \u2014 state key involved\n  expected_version int   \u2014 version caller held\n  actual_version  int|None \u2014 version in DB\n                           (None = key absent)\n\nConflict scenarios:\n  1. Version mismatch: another writer incremented\n     version between read and write\n  2. Key absent: CAS on non-existent key\n     (actual_version=None)\n\nCaller pattern (retry loop):\n  val, ver = state_get(...)  # read + note version\n  modified = transform(val)\n  state_compare_and_set(..., ver, modified)\n  # retry on CASConflictError",
      "originalText": "CASConflictError attributes:\n  key             str    \u2014 state key involved\n  expected_version int   \u2014 version caller held\n  actual_version  int|None \u2014 version in DB\n                           (None = key absent)\n\nConflict scenarios:\n  1. Version mismatch: another writer incremented\n     version between read and write\n  2. Key absent: CAS on non-existent key\n     (actual_version=None)\n\nCaller pattern (retry loop):\n  val, ver = state_get(...)  # read + note version\n  modified = transform(val)\n  state_compare_and_set(..., ver, modified)\n  # retry on CASConflictError",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#f87171",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 100029,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 100030,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.5
    },
